cafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"TV showcase design for home with contemporary aqua theme with rectangular upside cupboards\" class=\"wp-image-3941\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua-70x70.jpg 70w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/20235144\/tv-showcase-new-model-contemporary-aqua.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">&nbsp;A beautiful blend of blue and white gives this room a refreshing feel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploa